des:
Here you can listen to 100% rock around the clock. Whether it's 3 o'clock at night or 2 o'clock at noon, switch on and join in.

To play, simply say "Alexa, play Rock Radio" or "Alexa, start Rock Radio".
You can stop playback at any time by saying "Alexa, stop".

Want more information? We offer you the following options:

Alexa, ask Rock Radio Alexa, ask rock radio what was playing last
Alexa, ask Rock Radio what was playing last

The radio stream is provided by laut.fm, the social audio network.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
